#

Lemon Poppy Seed Waffles

25 min
$8.5
320 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastBrunchSweet

Description

Delightful and fluffy waffles infused with zesty lemon and crunchy poppy seeds, perfect for breakfast or brunch.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 ½ cups
  • sugar: ¼ cup
  • baking powder: 2 tsp
  • baking soda: ½ tsp
  • salt: ¼ tsp
  • milk: 1 cup
  • eggs: 2 large
  • unsalted butter: ½ cup
  • lemon zest: 2 tsp
  • poppy seeds: 2 tbsp
  • vanilla extract: 1 tsp
